Package org.apache.storm.jms

Interface JmsTupleProducer

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
JsonTupleProducer
public interface JmsTupleProducer extends Serializable
Interface to define classes that can produce a Storm Values objects from a jakarta.jms.Message object>.

Implementations are also responsible for declaring the output fields they produce.

If for some reason the implementation can't process a message (for example if it received a jakarta.jms.ObjectMessage when it was expecting a jakarta.jms.TextMessage it should return null to indicate to the JmsSpout that the message could not be processed.
